==Documentation==
This template creates a rating board page layout.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Rating Boards are organizations that rate video games (e.g., ESRB, PEGI, CERO).

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the rating board
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Image || Rating board logo
|-
|| Deck || Short description
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{RatingBoard
| Name = ESRB
| Guid = 3070-1
| Deck = The Entertainment Software Rating Board rates video games in North America...
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{RatingBoardEnd}}
</pre>
